					</article>
					<article class="suggestion">
						<a href=""><img src="/img/img_miniature_default.jpg" alt="a"></a>
						<h2><a href="">Title Publication</a></h2>
						<p>Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Molestiae nesciunt maxime est perspiciatis, eius omnis veniam fugit itaque consectetur. Ipsum sequi quisquam corrupti a explicabo inventore tempora saepe dignissimos odit.</p>
					</article>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section class="social_networks" id="$ontact">
				<a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCb636cFJPna9RYNgfPM2R7Q/videos" target="_black">YouTube</a>
				<a href="https://www.facebook.com/miguel.hurtado.3110" target="_black">facebook</a>
			</section>
			<% if (is_author) { %>
				<script src="js/create_article.js" type="module"></script>
			<% } else { %>
				<script src="js/modules/render_math.js" type="module"></script>
			<% } %>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>